document.full_text: prime minister yusuf raza gilani on monday rejected allegations that the killing of osama bin laden by u.s. troops in the country showed pakistani incompetence or complicity in hiding the al qaeda leader.
document.title: pakistan denies complicity, incompetence in bin laden case
